Dear Daniyah,


Selecting a graduate program is about more than finding a place to study; i=
t=E2=80=99s about finding a launchpad to set your ambition in motion. At th=
e George Washington University, we provide an immersive education that brid=
ges the distance between your potential and the world's most influential in=
stitutions.


Our diverse portfolio is designed to meet you where you are in your career.=
 Whether you are looking to lead with an [MBA](https://business.gwu.edu/mba=
), deep-dive into specialized knowledge with our [Master=E2=80=99s degrees]=
(https://business.gwu.edu/academics/graduate#specialized), or sharpen your =
edge through targeted [Graduate Certificates](https://business.gwu.edu/acad=
emics/certificates), we offer a pathway tailored to your trajectory.


Whether you are joining us from across the city or across the globe, you ar=
e just steps away from a community that transforms curiosity into monumenta=
l change. We invite you to join us for our upcoming GW School of Business V=
irtual Open House to see how our unique proximity to the heart of Washingto=
n, D.C., drives the progress of our students.


During this session, you will:


- Connect with our Vibrant Community: Hear from a panel of current graduate=
 students who are already using their GW experience to flourish and thrive.


- Explore Meaningful Outcomes: Learn how our career center services and spe=
cialized programs serve as a catalyst for your professional evolution.


- Navigate the Path Forward: Get incisive, savvy advice on our admission pr=
ocess to ensure you are ready to take the next step.


Master of Science in Artificial Intelligence for Business=C2=A0
We are thrilled to announce the launch of our newest degree. Designed for t=
he next generation of leaders, this program bridges the gap between cutting=
-edge AI technology and strategic business leadership. Be among the first t=
o explore this curriculum at our upcoming Open House.


**GW SCHOOL OF BUSINESS OPEN HOUSE**
**Friday, April 10, 2026**
10:00 a.m. - 12:15 p.m. ET
Online


[ Register Now](https://events.ringcentral.com/events/gwsb-graduate-open-ho=
use-april-10-2026)


We are a community with no borders and no limitations. We look forward to s=
howing you how, at GW Business, your goals are always within reach=E2=80=94=
and often just steps away.

Sincerely,

**The Graduate A****dmissions Team**
The George Washington University School of Business

